Nuclear Exit Will Cost EON Billions, Frankfurter Allgemeine Says

-- B y   R i c h a r d   W e i s s
-- 
2011-06-01T06:27:21Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-06-01/nuclear-exit-will-cost-eon-billions-frankfurter-allgemeine-says.html
Germany ’s plan to shut nuclear power
plants will cost EON AG a “double-digit billion euro amount,”
 Frankfurter Allgemeine Zeitung  said, citing Chief Executive
Officer Johannes Teyssen.  EON will seek compensation from the government, the
newspaper cited Teyssen as saying.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Richard Weiss in  Frankfurt  at 
 rweiss5@bloomberg.net .  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Benedikt Kammel at   bkammel@bloomberg.net . 